<item>
            <title>[TIKA-268] HTMLParser ommits necessary space-characters when parsing table-data </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-268</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When an HTML file with a table structure is given to the TIKA-ecosystem, then HTML parser doesn&apos;t output space characters between table cells.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Input&lt;br/&gt;
------------------------------&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;table&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;tr&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;td&amp;gt;Apache LUCENE&amp;lt;td&amp;gt;&amp;lt;td&amp;gt;is f****** amazing!&amp;lt;/td&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;/tr&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;tr&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;td&amp;gt;Apache TIKA&amp;lt;/td&amp;gt;&amp;lt;td&amp;gt;freaks you out!&amp;lt;/td&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;/tr&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;table&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Output&lt;br/&gt;
------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Apache LUCENEis f****** amazing!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Apache TIKAfreaks you out!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;unfortuantely i didnt have the time to do some investigation within HTMLParser.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Win, Mac, Lin; Java 5+&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
